# Crypto Average Price Calculator - Implementation Plan

## Context
Victor tracks crypto cost basis in BRL for Brazilian taxes using an Excel spreadsheet. He manually copies data from Crypto.com transaction reports, looks up PTAX exchange rates, and calculates average prices and profit/loss. This webapp automates that entire workflow as a pure frontend SPA.

## Tech Stack
- **React 19 + Vite + TypeScript** (SPA, no backend)
- **@tanstack/react-table v8** - headless datatable with sorting, filtering, column visibility
- **PapaParse** - CSV parsing (handles quoted commas in Crypto.com CSV)
- **Zustand** - lightweight state management
- **Tailwind CSS v4** - dark theme styling
- **lucide-react** - icons
- **pnpm** (per AGENTS.md)

