## Key Implementation Details
1. Crypto.com CSV header has trailing commas creating empty columns - parser must handle this
2. Running Balance in output has dollar formatting with commas (`" $1,064.61 "`) - re-import parser must strip
3. One trade order can produce multiple Trade Match IDs (multiple fills) - index must be 1:many
4. Transaction Quantity is already negative for sells/fees - use Math.abs() for BRL deductions
5. PTAX file dates are `ddmmyyyy` format, Crypto.com dates are `MM/DD/YYYY` - normalize to ISO
6. BRL columns show `R$ -` when no avg price seed exists - display as blank/dash, not zero
